        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-27 14:00:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-2\n\nWhy are we adding Sylvain and Krzysztof as commiters in this repo? Shouldn't only active contributors be mentioned there? Besides the ticket related in commit msg is closed and year old?",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "32d8fc67e451e7e012a90ad65cce30ae5070c2ce",
