          "username": "sdesbure"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-27 14:04:59.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Patch Set 4: Code-Review-2\n> \n> Why are we adding Sylvain and Krzysztof as commiters in this repo? Shouldn't only active contributors be mentioned there? Besides the ticket related in commit msg is closed and year old?\n\nHi Bartek, as acting PTL of OOM, I think I need to be here in order to manage the \"administrative commits\" (like this one which is pending for a while: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/oom/offline-installer/+/101352/).\n\nI added Krzysztof as he's a very active committer on main OOM repo but if it really hurts your feelings, I can remove...",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "ebbd66a8f878d699f6c5677180c260c193076e61",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5239,
          "name": "Mateusz Pilat",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "m.pilat@partner.samsung.com",
          "username": "m.pilat"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-27 14:39:54.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nI talked with Krzysztof, he has explained me why is that. Personally I am OK with that change. Just the form could be more transparent. Neither commit message nor a very old Jira ticket helps explain the need for this change.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "640783bd7e49e57cdf5ae11f85b1066c1ec90afa",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2319,
          "name": "Sylvain Desbureaux",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "sylvain.desbureaux@orange.com",
          "username": "sdesbure"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-27 14:43:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Patch Set 4:\n> \n> I talked with Krzysztof, he has explained me why is that. Personally I am OK with that change. Just the form could be more transparent. Neither commit message nor a very old Jira ticket helps explain the need for this change.\n\nYou're right Mateusz, I could have explain better and I apologize for that.\nAfter, it's really just for the \"administrative tasks\" and I don't plan to blindly merge / -2 the commits",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
